headline: ‘Time to Go Long on Bank Stocks’: Cantor Suggests 2 Names to Buy
summary: Expectations of interest rate cuts have led to some gains in the markets this month, showing that investors remain confident in the current rally. Overall, the year-to-date returns are impressive, even taking the springtime correction into account. The S&P 500 has gained 12% this year, and the NASDAQ is up ~16% over the same period.
